---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/sections/Header';
import Footer from '../../components/sections/Footer';
---

<BaseLayout
  lang="en"
  title="Legal Notice — FRONT Valencia"
  description="Legal notice and terms of use of the FRONT Restaurant website."
>
  <Header lang="en" client:load />
  <main id="main-content" class="pt-16">
    <section class="py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight text-text-primary mb-12">Legal Notice</h1>

      <div class="space-y-8 text-text-secondary">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-3 uppercase tracking-wide">Identification data</h2>
          <p>TODO-CONTENT: Owner identification data (company name, tax ID, registered address) pending client confirmation.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-3 uppercase tracking-wide">Purpose</h2>
          <p>This website aims to inform users about the services offered by FRONT, a restaurant and terrace located at La Marina de Valencia.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-3 uppercase tracking-wide">Intellectual property</h2>
          <p>All website content (text, images, trademarks, logos, source code) is the property of FRONT or third parties who have authorised its use, and is protected by current intellectual property legislation.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-3 uppercase tracking-wide">Limitation of liability</h2>
          <p>FRONT is not responsible for damages arising from misuse of the website, nor for information published by third parties through external links.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-3 uppercase tracking-wide">Applicable law</h2>
          <p>This legal notice is governed by current Spanish and European legislation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer lang="en" client:load />
</BaseLayout>
